      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * Marvin</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Marvin_the_robot_is_disappointed.gif\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2d/Marvin_the_robot_is_disappointed.gif/330px-Marvin_the_robot_is_disappointed.gif\" width=\"300\" height=\"232\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2d/Marvin_the_robot_is_disappointed.gif/500px-Marvin_the_robot_is_disappointed.gif 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/2d/Marvin_the_robot_is_disappointed.gif 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Marvin_the_robot_is_disappointed.gif\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marvin_the_Paranoid_Android\">Marvin the robot</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Marvin</b>,<br />\nan <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> and <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> compatible chess engine by <a href=\"/Martin_Danielsson\" title=\"Martin Danielsson\">Martin Danielsson</a>, written in <a href=\"/C\" title=\"C\">C</a>. \nMarvin was originally developed in the early 2000s until 2005, released in May 2004 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> and January 2005 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> as closed source engine. \nAfter ten years \"out of business\", Martin Danielsson restarted the development in 2015 -  the completely rewritten Marvin <b>2.0.0</b> was released as <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source engine</a> under the terms of the <a href=\"/Free_Software_Foundation#GPL\" title=\"Free Software Foundation\">GNU General Public License</a> (GPL3) in March 2017 <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Features\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Features</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Board_Representation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Board Representation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Search\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Search</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Evaluation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Evaluation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#2004_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2004 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#2017_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2017 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#Chess_Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-13\"><a href=\"#Misc_2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-14\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Features\">Features</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marvin&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Features\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Board_Representation\"><a href=\"/Board_Representation\" title=\"Board Representation\">Board Representation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marvin&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Board Representation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/8x8_Board\" title=\"8x8 Board\">8x8 Board</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards#Plain\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Plain Magic Bitboards</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Search\"><a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marvin&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Search\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><l